    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that's been well-loved? This car is in great shape and ready for its next adventure! It\u2019s been super dependable for me, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love how smoothly it handles. It\u2019s got plenty of life left and is just waiting for a new home. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions\u2014I'd love to chat!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist-spec example featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, equipped with individual throttle bodies and a soaring 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a tactile Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis benefits from reinforced rear subframe mounts, mitigating common floor-pan fatigue and ensuring structural integrity under high lateral loads. Recent mechanical sorting includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and shim-and-bucket valve adjustment to maintain peak volumetric efficiency. While the exterior shows minor patina consistent with its mileage, the drivetrain remains exceptionally tight, offering the sharp throttle response and balanced weight distribution this chassis is renowned for.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Used car in good condition. Regular maintenance performed. Clean title. Minor cosmetic wear. Runs well.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presented here is a well-cared-for vehicle that offers a fantastic driving experience without the 'new car' price tag. The exterior paint holds a beautiful gloss, though you will find a few minor, expected stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side wheel rim. The interior is exceptionally clean and has been kept in a smoke-free, pet-free environment. The leather seats are supple and free of tears, showing only light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every button and feature works perfectly, from the heated seats to the premium sound system and navigation. Under the hood, the engine is dry and runs quietly. I have kept a detailed log of all services, including a recent transmission fluid flush and a fresh set of all-season tires with plenty of tread remaining. The car tracks straight and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. This is a dependable, honest vehicle ready for many more miles of service.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptionally well-maintained executive vehicle, which stands as a testament to diligent ownership and consistent mechanical care. This automobile has undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for performance and safety. The exterior retains a professional luster, while the interior remains refined and inviting. Offering a superior driving experience and a sophisticated aesthetic, this vehicle represents a premier opportunity for those who demand excellence and reliability in their automotive selection.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty ride. It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and is still in really solid shape! It runs great and has plenty of life left in it for all your adventures. It's not brand new, but it's been well-loved and is totally ready to hit the road with a new owner. Swing by and take it for a spin\u2014you're going to love how it drives!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust BMW E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine featuring individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. This example is equipped with the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual transmission, ensuring a visceral connection to the M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis has been maintained with precision, including essential subframe reinforcement and a refreshed cooling system to handle the thermal demands of the 8,000 RPM redline. While the exterior displays minor road-derived patina, the aerodynamic profile remains sharp, and the suspension geometry provides the telepathic handling and lateral stability expected of this iconic platform. A true enthusiast's specimen optimized for spirited driving.",
